---
import testingVideo from "../assets/video/testingVideo.mp4";
import measure1 from "../assets/img/product/measureFrontV2.avif";
import measure2 from "../assets/img/product/measureSide.avif";
import iconGlasses from "../assets/img/icons/iconGlasses.webp";
import peopleUsingGlasses from "../assets/img/peopleUsingGlasses-desktop.avif";
---
<section id="features" class="py-4 md:pt-0 lg:py-5 xl:flex xl:justify-center">
  <div class="container px-4 md:px-6">
    <!-- divide here -->
     <section class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-2xl  bg-gradient-to-br from-white/10 to-white/5 backdrop-blur-md border-white/20 group border-2 p-4 px-4 lg:p-8 flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-6 lg:gap-8 mt-10 mb-6 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Subtle background effect -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-amber-400/5 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
  
  <div class="textContainer flex flex-col p-2 lg:self-center lg:flex-1 relative z-10">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-center lg:text-left mb-4 leading-tight">
      Ve la <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-300 to-orange-400">Protección Real</span> en Acción
    </h2>
    
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-center lg:text-left max-w-2xl mb-6 leading-relaxed text-brand-body">
      No confíes solo en nuestra palabra. Esta demostración muestra exactamente cómo nuestras lentes bloquean la luz azul dañina. 
    </p>
    
    <!-- Key benefits list -->
    <ul class="space-y-3 mb-3 max-w-xl">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <span class="text-amber-300 text-xl mt-0.5">✓</span>
        <span class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-100"><strong>Protección visible:</strong> La tarjeta sensible cambia de color donde NO hay protección</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <span class="text-amber-300 text-xl mt-0.5">✓</span>
        <span class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-100"><strong>Área protegida intacta:</strong> Nuestras lentes bloquean completamente la luz azul</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <span class="text-amber-300 text-xl mt-0.5">✓</span>
        <span class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-100"><strong>Pruébalo tú mismo:</strong> Incluimos la tarjeta de prueba con el led de luz azul en cada pedido</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
    
    
  </div>

  <div class="videoContainer flex flex-col items-center justify-center lg:flex-1.5 xl:flex-1">
        <video class="rounded-xl shadow-lg w-full opacity-80 max-w-2xl mb-2 md:w-[40%] lg:w-[100%] xl:w-[60%]" autoplay loop muted playsinline>
          <source src={testingVideo} type="video/mp4" />
          Tu navegador no soporta la reproducción de video.
        </video>
        <!-- Gift callout box -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-500/20 to-orange-500/20 border-2 border-yellow-400/40 rounded-xl p-4 md:p-5 shadow-lg mt-3">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-2">
        <span class="text-3xl"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#ffffff" class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-filled icon-tabler-gift"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M11 14v8h-4a3 3 0 0 1 -3 -3v-4a1 1 0 0 1 1 -1h6zm8 0a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v4a3 3 0 0 1 -3 3h-4v-8h6zm-2.5 -12a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 3.163 5h.337a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v1a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2h-7v-5h-2v5h-7a2 2 0 0 1 -2 -2v-1a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h.337a3.486 3.486 0 0 1 -.337 -1.5c0 -1.933 1.567 -3.5 3.483 -3.5c1.755 -.03 3.312 1.092 4.381 2.934l.136 .243c1.033 -1.914 2.56 -3.114 4.291 -3.175l.209 -.002zm-9 2a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 0 3h3.143c-.741 -1.905 -1.949 -3.02 -3.143 -3zm8.983 0c-1.18 -.02 -2.385 1.096 -3.126 3h3.143a1.5 1.5 0 1 0 -.017 -3z" /></svg></span>
        <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-yellow-100 text-center">REGALO INCLUIDO</h3>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-100 leading-relaxed">
        Recibe tu propia <strong>tarjeta de prueba profesional</strong> junto con el <strong>led de luz azul</strong> y verifica la protección tu mismo desde casa.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  
</section>

  <div class="grid gap-8 mt-12 md:mt-12 lg:grid-cols-4 xl:px-20 md:flex md:flex-col md:items-center">
  <section class="py-5 md:py-16 lg:py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto md:px-6 max-w-7xl">
    
    {/* Section Header */}
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center gap-6 mb-12 lg:mb-16">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 py-1 px-3 rounded-full bg-amber-500/10 border border-amber-500/30">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#f59e0b" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-ruler"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M5 4h14a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v5a1 1 0 0 1 -1 1h-7a1 1 0 0 0 -1 1v7a1 1 0 0 1 -1 1h-5a1 1 0 0 1 -1 -1v-14a1 1 0 0 1 1 -1" /><path d="M4 8l2 0" /><path d="M4 12l3 0" /><path d="M4 16l2 0" /><path d="M8 4l0 2" /><path d="M12 4l0 3" /><path d="M16 4l0 2" /></svg>
        <span class="text-xs lg:text-sm font-semibold text-amber-400 uppercase tracking-wide">
          Especificaciones Técnicas
        </span>
      </div>
      
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight">
        Diseño Ergonómico y Cómodo Para Uso Prolongado
      </h2>
      
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
        Montura ligera de <span class="text-white font-semibold">alta calidad</span> diseñada para adaptarse cómodamente durante jornadas extensas de trabajo o estudio.
      </p>
    </div>

    {/* Specifications Cards Grid */}
    <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2 xl:gap-12">
      
      {/* Card 1: Front View */}
      <div class="relative group">
        {/* Card Container with White Background */}
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-gray-100  rounded-2xl shadow-2xl border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-amber-500/20 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.02]">
          
          {/* Label Badge */}
          <div class="absolute -top-3 left-6 z-20">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-500 to-orange-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-full font-bold text-sm shadow-lg">
              Vista Frontal
            </div>
          </div>

          {/* Image Container */}
          <div class="relative flex items-center justify-center">
            <img 
              src={measure1.src} 
              alt="Medidas gafas Amber Vision - Vista frontal"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover drop-shadow-2xl"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>

          {/* Specifications List */}
          <div class="space-y-4 p-5 pt-6 border-t border-gray-300">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-amber-500/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#f59e0b" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-ruler-3"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M19.875 8c.621 0 1.125 .512 1.125 1.143v5.714c0 .631 -.504 1.143 -1.125 1.143h-15.875a1 1 0 0 1 -1 -1v-5.857c0 -.631 .504 -1.143 1.125 -1.143h15.75" /><path d="M9 8v2" /><path d="M6 8v3" /><path d="M12 8v3" /><path d="M18 8v3" /><path d="M15 8v2" /></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Ancho Total - <span class="text-gray-700 text-sm">14.5 cm</span > </p>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Diseño universal que se adapta a la mayoría de rostros</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-amber-500/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#f59e0b">
                  <path d="M12 2a10 10 0 1 0 10 10A10 10 0 0 0 12 2zm0 18a8 8 0 1 1 8-8 8 8 0 0 1-8 8z"/>
                  <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Lentes Amplias - <span class="text-gray-700 text-sm">5.3 cm</span> </p>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Máxima cobertura y protección para tus ojos</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Card 2: Side View */}
      <div class="relative group">
        {/* Card Container with White Background */}
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-gray-100  rounded-2xl shadow-2xl border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-amber-500/20 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.02]">
          
          {/* Label Badge */}
          <div class="absolute -top-3 left-6 z-10">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-500 to-orange-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-full font-bold text-sm shadow-lg">
              Vista Lateral
            </div>
          </div>

          {/* Image Container */}
          <div class="relative aspect-[4/2.5] flex items-center justify-center">
            <img 
              src={measure2.src} 
              alt="Medidas gafas Amber Vision - Vista lateral"
              class="w-full h-full object-contain drop-shadow-2xl"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>

          {/* Specifications List */}
          <div class="space-y-4 p-5 pt-6 border-t border-gray-300">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-amber-500/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#f59e0b">
                  <path d="M12 2v20M17 7l-5-5-5 5M17 17l-5 5-5-5"/>
                </svg>
                
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Patillas Ajustables - <span class="text-gray-700 text-sm">14.8 cm</span></p>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Se adaptan cómodamente sin presionar detrás de las orejas</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-amber-500/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#f59e0b" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-weight"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M9 6a3 3 0 1 0 6 0a3 3 0 1 0 -6 0" /><path d="M6.835 9h10.33a1 1 0 0 1 .984 .821l1.637 9a1 1 0 0 1 -.984 1.179h-13.604a1 1 0 0 1 -.984 -1.179l1.637 -9a1 1 0 0 1 .984 -.821" /></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Peso Ultra Ligero - <span class="text-gray-700 text-sm">26 gr</span ></p>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Úsalas durante horas sin sentir presión ni molestias</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  </section>
    <section class="pt-5 md:py-10">
  <div class="container mx-auto md:px-6 max-w-7xl">
    
    {/* Section Header */}
    <div class="text-center mb-12 lg:mb-16">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/30 mb-6">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#05df72" class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-filled icon-tabler-circle-check"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path><path d="M17 3.34a10 10 0 1 1 -14.995 8.984l-.005 -.324l.005 -.324a10 10 0 0 1 14.995 -8.336zm-1.293 5.953a1 1 0 0 0 -1.32 -.083l-.094 .083l-3.293 3.292l-1.293 -1.292l-.094 -.083a1 1 0 0 0 -1.403 1.403l.083 .094l2 2l.094 .083a1 1 0 0 0 1.226 0l.094 -.083l4 -4l.083 -.094a1 1 0 0 0 -.083 -1.32z"></path></svg>
        <span class="text-xs lg:text-sm font-semibold text-green-400 uppercase tracking-wide">
          Comodidad Garantizada
        </span>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 leading-tight">
        Tan Cómodas Que Olvidarás Que Las Llevas Puestas
      </h2>
      
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-brand-body max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Diseñadas para quienes pasan horas frente a pantallas. <span class="text-brand-headline font-semibold">Sin presión, sin marcas, sin molestias.</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    {/* Main Content Card */}
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white/10 to-white/5 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/20 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl hover:border-amber-500/30 transition-all">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-0">
        
        {/* Text Content */}
        <div class="p-2 lg:p-12 flex flex-col justify-center order-2 lg:order-1">
          
          {/* Feature List */}
          <div class="space-y-6 mb-8">
            
            {/* Feature 1 */}
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500 to-orange-600 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white">
                  <path d="M12 2a10 10 0 1 0 10 10A10 10 0 0 0 12 2zm0 18a8 8 0 1 1 8-8 8 8 0 0 1-8 8z"/>
                  <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">
                  Diseño Clásico y Atemporal
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                  Inspiradas en los marcos más icónicos de la historia, con líneas limpias que se ven profesionales en cualquier contexto: oficina, universidad o casa.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            {/* Feature 2 */}
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-emerald-600 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white">
                  <path d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">
                  Material TR90 de Grado Premium
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                  Fabricadas con <strong class="text-white">TR90</strong>, el mismo material usado en gafas deportivas de alta gama. Ultra ligeras, flexibles y prácticamente irrompibles.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            {/* Feature 3 */}
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-cyan-600 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white">
                  <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm0 18c-4.41 0-8-3.59-8-8s3.59-8 8-8 8 3.59 8 8-3.59 8-8 8zm-1-13h2v6h-2zm0 8h2v2h-2z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">
                  Se Ajustan a Tu Rostro, No Al Revés
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                  Las varillas flexibles se adaptan suavemente a diferentes tamaños de cabeza sin generar presión detrás de las orejas, incluso después de 8+ horas de uso continuo.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>

          {/* Trust Badge */}
          <div class="bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/30 rounded-xl p-4 flex items-center gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#05df72" class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-filled icon-tabler-circle-check"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path><path d="M17 3.34a10 10 0 1 1 -14.995 8.984l-.005 -.324l.005 -.324a10 10 0 0 1 14.995 -8.336zm-1.293 5.953a1 1 0 0 0 -1.32 -.083l-.094 .083l-3.293 3.292l-1.293 -1.292l-.094 -.083a1 1 0 0 0 -1.403 1.403l.083 .094l2 2l.094 .083a1 1 0 0 0 1.226 0l.094 -.083l4 -4l.083 -.094a1 1 0 0 0 -.083 -1.32z"></path></svg>
            <p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm md:text-base">
              Usadas por +3,000 profesionales que valoran comodidad y estilo
            </p>
          </div>

        </div>

        {/* Image Column */}
        <div class="relative h-[400px] lg:h-full order-1 lg:order-2">
          <img 
            src={peopleUsingGlasses.src} 
            alt="Profesionales usando gafas Amber Vision en diferentes contextos"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          {/* Overlay Badge */}
          <div class="absolute bottom-[40%] left-[17%] bg-black/20 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-4 px-2 border border-white/20 w-max">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col items-center">
                <p class="text-brand-headline font-semibold text-sm text-center w-[80%]">
                  Estilo Universal
                </p>
                <p class="text-brand-body text-xs text-center">
                  Para hombres y mujeres de todas las edades
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
  </div>
  </div>
</section>
